  "body": "This issue tracks epoch processing optimization. Current implementation is straight up from the spec with a few instances of O(n^2) complexity. \r\n\r\nOptimization can be done via 1 iteration over active validators for basic info, then 1 iteration over pending attestations to collect vote stats, and 1 iteration over validator to compute for balances. This shortens run time to O(V + A) where V is the length of validator list and A is the length of the pending attestations in state",
